<h2>Oridium</h2>
<img src="http://www.dicts.info/img/ud/c/chalcopyrite.jpg" width="200" align="right">
<p>Oridium is a rare ore, yellowish gold in color.  It's mined primarily in the Belt of Arah.  A few planets directly outside the asteroid belt also have deposits of the Ore.</p>

<p>The largest galactic purchaser of Oridium is the Galactic Empire (EMP), who also holds a 24.7% share interest in <a href="index.cfm?pin=odi">Oridelve Incorporated (ODI)</a>, the largest supplier.</p>
